---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="On Stage at South Summit: Europe's Leading Startup Conference | Francisco Cucullu" description="Main stage pitch at South Summit, one of Europe's top startup conferences.">
    <article class="wrapper">
        <a href="/blog" class="back">&larr; Back</a>

        <header class="article-header">
            <span class="tag">Pitch</span>
            <h1>On Stage at South Summit: Europe's Leading Startup Conference</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Pitching on the main stage and being interviewed by media at one of Europe's top startup events.</p>
            <p class="meta">By Francisco Cucullu &middot; AI Product Leader</p>
        </header>

        <div class="content">
            <p>South Summit is one of the most important startup conferences in Europe, bringing together thousands of founders, investors, and corporate leaders. I had the opportunity to pitch on the main stage and was interviewed by media on-site.</p>

            <p>The main stage at South Summit is a high-pressure environment. Hundreds of people in the audience, a strict time limit, and a panel of experienced investors evaluating every word. Preparation for this kind of event is intense. You rehearse the pitch dozens of times, anticipate every possible question, and refine your delivery until it feels natural.</p>

            <div class="video-wrapper">
                <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/i2spr2QhaGM" title="South Summit Pitch" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>

            <p>Beyond the pitch itself, South Summit is valuable for the connections it creates. The hallway conversations, the investor meetings, and the spontaneous encounters with other founders are where real relationships form. Some of the most productive partnerships I have built started with a handshake at events like this one.</p>

            <p>Competing at this level taught me that confidence on stage comes from knowing your numbers cold and believing in the problem you are solving. If you truly understand the pain your users feel, the pitch writes itself.</p>
        </div>

        
            <div class="photo-grid">
                <img src="/assets/speaking-1779160559702-AQADXgxrG04GYER-.jpg" alt="Francisco Cucullu speaking" />
                <img src="/assets/speaking-1779160537307-AQADXQxrG04GYER-.jpg" alt="Francisco Cucullu speaking" />
                <img src="/assets/speaking-1779160577814-AQADYQxrG04GYER-.jpg" alt="Francisco Cucullu speaking" />
                <img src="/assets/speaking-1779160570482-AQADYAxrG04GYER9.jpg" alt="Francisco Cucullu speaking" />
            </div>

        <div class="article-links">
            <a href="/speaking/south-summit" class="link-button">View event page</a>
        </div>

        <footer class="article-footer">
            <p>Francisco Cucullu is an AI Product Leader building AI products at scale. <a href="/">Learn more</a>.</p>
        </footer>
    </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .wrapper {
        max-width: 720px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    }

    .back {
        color: #a855f7;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: var(--text-sm);
        display: inline-block;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .article-header {
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .tag {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
        border-radius: 999rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        background: var(--accent-regular);
        color: var(--accent-text-over);
        display: inline-block;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: var(--text-3xl);
        color: var(--gray-0);
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .subtitle {
        font-size: var(--text-lg);
        color: var(--gray-300);
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .meta {
        color: var(--gray-400);
        font-size: var(--text-sm);
    }

    .content {
        color: var(--gray-200);
        line-height: 1.8;
        font-size: var(--text-md);
    }

    .content h2 {
        font-size: var(--text-2xl);
        color: var(--gray-0);
        margin-top: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .content p {
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .content a {
        color: #a855f7;
    }

    .video-wrapper {
        position: relative;
        padding-bottom: 56.25%;
        height: 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        border-radius: 0.75rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .video-wrapper iframe {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .article-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .link-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.6rem 1.25rem;
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        background: var(--accent-regular);
        color: var(--accent-text-over);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: var(--text-sm);
        transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }

    .link-button:hover {
        opacity: 0.85;
    }

    
    .photo-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 1rem;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
    }

    .photo-grid img {
        width: 100%;
        border-radius: 0.75rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
        object-fit: cover;
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
    }

    .article-footer {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        padding-top: 2rem;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
        color: var(--gray-400);
        font-size: var(--text-sm);
    }

    .article-footer a {
        color: #a855f7;
    }

    @media (min-width: 50em) {
        h1 {
            font-size: var(--text-4xl);
        }
    }
</style>
